        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Concerning selection of lots in Matagorda.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>Dr Sir,</p>

<p><persName>Mr. Hoit</persName> informs me that you wish me to instruct you where I
wish the blocks located that I shall be entitled to take in <placeName>Matagorda</placeName>
I have not time to go there, and must request that you will locate
them for me&#8212; I shall be satisfied with your selection, I want
nothing but a fair chance with the rest.</p>

<p><persName>S. F. Austin  </persName>  [Rubric]</p>

<p><date when="1832-10-08">Oct. 8. 1832</date></p>
<p><persName>Mr E Wightman</persName></p>

<p>[Addressed:]<persName> Mr. E. R. Wightman </persName>  <placeName>Matagorda</placeName></p>


        </div1>
